snippet.title: The Taller I Grow [Trailer]
snippet.description:
The Taller I Grow is a short indie game where you connect to objects in your environment to solve puzzles in 30 levels. This game will test your patience, problem solving abilities, and reflexes.

Now available for free on PC/Mac:
http://noobles-studio.itch.io/the-taller-i-grow

Follow me on social media to see development updates and other things related to game development:
itch.io: http://noobles-studio.itch.io/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/noobles.studio/?hl=en
Twitter: https://twitter.com/noobles_studio
Website: https://nooblesstudio.com

If you have any questions, comments, or concerns, contact us at support@nooblesstudio.com.
